article.headline: Wagner 74, LIU Brooklyn 64
article.story: NEW YORK (AP) -- Nigel Wyatte had 19 points and 14 rebounds to help Wagner beat LIU 74-64 on Thursday night in a Northeast Conference game. Teoine Carroll added 12 points for the Seahawks (8-13, 5-6). Brandon Thomas scored 22 points for the Blackbirds (7-14, 3-9), and James Williams had 14. The Seahawks took the lead for good at 62-60 on Wyatte's layup with 1:30 left.
